{"tid":2184794,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西記者：美斯是史上最大背叛 船在沉他跳船逃跑","createTime":"2020-09-02T00:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T10:51:58.000Z","uid":25345,"like":11,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d29510a6e55d836c4916ba4d993e9eb904065e5e","tid":2184794,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:10:54.000Z","msg":"西班牙記者伊度-奧吉雷稱，美斯如今要求離隊的舉動，是足球歷史上最大的背叛。<br />\n<br />\n  奧吉雷在西班牙電視節目《El Chiringuito de Jugones》中說：「在我看來，美斯所做的，是足球歷史上最大的背叛。」<br />\n<br />\n  「巴塞隆拿的球迷們不該受到這種對待，美斯在拋棄他們。」<br />\n<br />\n  「現在美斯應該召開一次新聞記者會，說：我將要留下，因為我在這裡有美好記憶，我知道這傢俱樂部對我意味著什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n  「當這艘船在沉沒時，美斯卻要跳船逃跑，他不應該現在離開。」"},{"pid":"397ce31b0b88ed7ad0ee8b7c69f79d8a7f30760a","tid":2184794,"uid":92603,"like":40,"dislike":5,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"幫你風光十幾年<br />\n球員生涯最後兩三年走=背叛"},{"pid":"34c98cd3b88dc796be13379b917d657e38d26306","tid":2184794,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:17:03.000Z","msg":"反而覺得美斯似當年嘅古天奴"},{"pid":"0e55f272fde36b7d2f91395c67a1207ab8c91021","tid":2184794,"uid":6116,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:17:07.000Z","msg":"唔係船沉小花走 <br />\n係小花走船沉"},{"pid":"413c9177f3fc026d329e44c32498ba617c8301ff","tid":2184794,"uid":133545,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"入黎睇疤迷留言的"},{"pid":"aa9cdb511e4788bf9e6283fc81161dfc07cf22e2","tid":2184794,"uid":158499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34c98cd3b88dc796be13379b917d657e38d26306","tid":2184794,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:17:03.000Z","msg":"反而覺得美斯似當年嘅古天奴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:19:30.000Z","msg":"搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8437fccc971f24e3ca1889696e017be3c01e0553","tid":2184794,"uid":158499,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"0e55f272fde36b7d2f91395c67a1207a